<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467260' id='t-467260'>someone who was essentially
mentally ill and broke</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469660' id='t-469660'>to get money to then 
pay for weapons</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471879' id='t-471879'>that they could then charge him
