</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='474387' id='t-474387'>TR: One final question.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476514' id='t-476514'>Less than 10 days ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478035' id='t-478035'>the FBI arrested some potential 
