<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='484725' id='t-484725'>and were those real,
or examples of more of the same?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='487622' id='t-487622'>TA: Well so far, we only know
